scheduled_maintenances.name: Scheduled Maintenance for the US & EU Regions - September 6th 22:00 UTC to 22:30 UTC

incident_updates.body:
We intend to perform maintenance on Saturday, September 6th from 22:00 UTC to 22:30 UTC (or Saturday, September 6th from 15:00 PDT to 15:30 PDT). Customers in the US & EU regions can expect a short service interruption at some point during this timeframe which may include anomalies for New Relic as described below:
- inability to render the New Relic UI
- inability to complete new sign ups or modify account structures.

Please note, we do not anticipate impact to data ingest or alert notifications at this time. All further updates will be posted here on our status page.
